<inglise> Plants for the incineration of hazardous wastes shall be operated in order to achieve a level of incineration as complete as possible. </inglise>
<eesti> Ohtlike j&auml;&auml;tmete p&otilde;letusrajatisi k&auml;itatakse nii, et p&otilde;lemine oleks v&otilde;imalikult t&auml;ielik. </eesti>
